Cody strode forward confidently, forging into the darkness, ready for anything. Anything, that was, except for the
dirty claw that came swiping out of the shadows ahead of him, scoring his chest and arm as he belatedly tried to twist
out of the way. From the way it moved, not to mention the stench, it was almost certainly a zombie. As it lurched
closer, Cody recognized it as originally having been a kobold -- perhaps the very same kobold that had attacked him not
far from here.
